{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"handlePushRegistration:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSData","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSData"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"deviceToken"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The device token Data received from APNs","type":"text"}]}],"name":"deviceToken"}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Call this method from your AppDelegate’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"application:didRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithDeviceToken:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to forward the device token to Pushwoosh."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The SDK normally handles this automatically via method swizzling, but you may need to call"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this directly if:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You’ve disabled swizzling"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You’re managing multiple push providers","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You need custom token processing"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Example","anchor":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Manual token handling with multiple push providers:","type":"text"}]},{"code":["class AppDelegate: UIResponder, UIApplicationDelegate {","","    func application(_ application: UIApplication,","                    didRegisterForRemoteNotificationsWithDeviceToken deviceToken: Data) {","","        \/\/ Convert token to string for logging","        let tokenString = deviceToken.map { String(format: \"%02.2hhx\", $0) }.joined()","        Logger.info(\"Received APNs token: \\(tokenString.prefix(20))...\")","","        \/\/ Send to Pushwoosh","        Pushwoosh.configure.handlePushRegistration(deviceToken)","","        \/\/ Send to other push providers if needed","        FirebaseMessaging.messaging().apnsToken = deviceToken","","        \/\/ Sync with backend","        BackendAPI.shared.updatePushToken(tokenString)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Only use this method if you need manual control.","type":"text"}]}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"handlePushRegistration:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"handlePushRegistration:","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)handlePushRegistration:","title":"handlePushRegistration:"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/handlePushRegistration:"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Manually handles the device push token registration."}],"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/handlepushregistration:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/P